### Configuration — change BASE_URL to match your running environment
@BASE_URL = http://localhost:8080

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 1. Browse first page of orders
###    Look at each item.productSnapshot: should never be null.
###    Expected shape: { name, price, categories: [{id, name}] }
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/orders?page=0&size=5
Accept: application/json

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 2. Second page — spot-check more items
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/orders?page=1&size=5
Accept: application/json

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 3. Deep page — verifies backfill reached rows created long ago
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/orders?page=100&size=5
Accept: application/json
